name: Model Dish: The Usual Selection
description: This delicately crafted model dish is based on the famous food from Natlan, the Tataco, and is made from cloth, metal, and Peach Palm Wood.\nThey say that Tatacos are renowned for versatility of style and convenience, making them a top choice for customers and competitors alike to quickly replenish energy. Additionally, its simplicity in preparation allows vendors to serve it rapidly, making it one of the most popular foods in the Stadium of the Sacred Flame.
